⠀              ⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⡤⣴⣶⠞⠋⠉⠉⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠁⠈⠉⠉⠙⠻⢿⣿⣗⡢⢤⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
              ⠀⠀⠀⣠⢊⣵⠞⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠓⢭⣳⣮⣳⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀              ⠀⣼⣿⠏⠀        ⠀'Hey, you. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⢿⣮⡙⢷⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
